  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You are skilled at fighting without the confines of armor. You gain the following benefits:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>While you are wearing light or no armor and not wielding a shield, you can use your bonus action to mark a target within 30 feet that you can see until the end of your next turn. When you do so, you gain a bonus to AC and Dexterity saving throws against effects the target controls equal to half your Dexterity modifier (minimum of +1) while marked. You can only have one creature marked in this way at a time.</li>\n<li>You have advantage on Dexterity checks and Dexterity saving throws to avoid being moved.</li></ul>",
